parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflators can cause the airbag to deploy incorrectly, leading to serious injury or death. The delay in repairing or replacing the defective airbag inflators can increase the risk of accidents and fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light may be illuminated
the airbag may deploy incorrectly
or the vehicle may be deemed unsafe to drive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of replacement parts for the Takata airbag recall can lead to a delay in repairing or replacing the defective airbag inflators, increasing the risk of accidents and fatalities.
symptoms: Dealerships may not have the necessary parts to complete the recall repair
leading to a delay in scheduling the repair or a lack of communication from the manufacturer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the frame can cause the structural integrity of the vehicle to fail, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Spare tire stabilizing bracket rusted away and fell off
rear shackles for the springs broke on both sides
frame rusted apart
bed of the truck rusted away
cross members broke
gas tank was in danger of falling off
severe rust on the entire back half of the truck
frame and undercarriage rusted
rear spring shackle rusted through and broke off
frame cracked off
spring hanger rusted out
frame is completely rusted out.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear spring shackle can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Rear spring shackle rusted through and broke off
rear shackle attachment looks like it's going to fail
rear spring shackle rusted and broken
rear shackle hanger rusted out
rear spring shackle fell apart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wheel bearing can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Front wheel bearing failed
wheel began to shift sideways abnormally
steering wheel became difficult to maneuver
front passenger side wheel was emitting smoke and partially detached from the vehicle
whining noise coming from the front of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the frame can lead to structural failure, causing the spare tire to fall off, the bed to collapse, or the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The frame is rusted or corroded
the spare tire is loose or has fallen off
the bed is rusted or has holes
the cross member is rusted or broken
the brake lines are rusted
the vehicle is unable to pass inspection.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear frame crossmember can cause the spare tire to fall off, the bed to collapse, or the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The rear frame crossmember is rusted or broken
the spare tire is loose or has fallen off
the bed is rusted or has holes
the fuel emission control tubing is damaged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch can cause the door to open unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents or injuries, especially in the event of a rollover.
symptoms: The door latch is defective
the door will not stay latched
the door ajar light is on
the dome light is on.
